<h2>Project Challenges & Solutions</h2>

<div class="challenge-box">
    <strong>Challenge 1: Timely Vulnerability Notification</strong>
    <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Delays in alerting resource owners about new vulnerabilities</p>
    <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Automated detection and email notifications via Logic Apps and Function Apps</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Result:</strong> 95% reduction in notification time</p>
</div>

<div class="challenge-box">
    <strong>Challenge 2: Remediation Tracking & Accountability</strong>
    <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Lack of visibility and follow-up on unresolved vulnerabilities</p>
    <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Centralized tracking in Azure Storage Tables</li>
        <li>Automated weekly reminders with SOPs</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Result:</strong> 80% increase in timely vulnerability remediation</p>
</div>

<div class="challenge-box">
    <strong>Challenge 3: Enforcing Compliance</strong>
    <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Persistent vulnerabilities despite repeated notifications</p>
    <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Automated enforcement by removing non-compliant ACR images after three reminders</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Result:</strong> 100% compliance for critical vulnerabilities</p>
</div>

